observationText: The HSC1λ cell line was derived from a human malignant peripheral nerve sheath tumor (MPNST) and harbors a homozygous NF1 nonsense mutation (c.2041C>T, p.Arg681*).
The HSC1λ cell line exhibited a homozygous deletion of the CDKN2A locus, which is frequently inactivated in MPNSTs.
The HSC1λ cell line exhibited a homozygous deletion of the CDKN2B locus in addition to CDKN2A.
